text: Primals spread across the entire galaxy.
A galaxy-wide war occurs then all primals vanish.
Earth has first contact with an alien species thousands of years ago.
The 50 solars countdown starts for Earth to file an appeal for mineral and element rights.
Odette loses her legs within a dungeon. She is given a floating disc that allows her to attach her torso to other creatures.
Odette becomes Mordecai's guildmaster.
Odette becomes Mordecai's manager.
Mordecai becomes a Changeling Arcanist.
Mordecai's brother, Uzzi, becomes a Skyfowl Storm Commander.
2,000 cycles prior to the premier of Dungeon Crawler World: Earth, Mordecai becomes a guildmaster.
250 cycles prior to the premier of Dungeon Crawler World: Earth, the Blood Sultanate of the Nagas are bankrupted by hosting a crawl and giving out 18 celestial loot boxes.
The Syndicate advance team arrives on Earth in the 1930s.
The preparation phase for Dungeon Crawler World: Earth starts in 1964.
The Valtay Corporation arrives outside of the Sol system in anticipation of collecting on the Borant Corporation's debt.

The Borant Corporation is pressured by its government to start Dungeon Crawler World: Earth early and finish it quickly as a way to get the patron, advertising, tourism, and elite monster sponsorship money as soon as possible to hold off bankruptcy seizure of the Borant Corporation by the Syndicate.
Agatha starts a fire outside of the Meadow Lark Retirement home in Wenatchee Washington.
Beatrice goes to the Bahamas with one of her ex-boyfriend Brad. Carl sees a picture of them being intimate on Instagram and breaks up with Bea.
The Borant Corporation begins mining Earth for elemental deposits.
Dungeon Crawler World: Earth opens on Earth per the Mined Material Reclamation act and subsection 35 of the Indigenous Planetary Species Protection Act.
The 18-level World Dungeon opens.
Mordecai changes into a Rat Hooligan.
